---
title: Italian Sausage Cavatappi with Herbed Ricotta
description: Grab some napkins and prepare yourself for a bowl of sheer comfort. Savoury Italian sausage takes centre stage in this hearty pasta with  baby spinach and a generous dollop of creamy herbed ricotta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cavatappis-a-la-saucisse-italienne-9eaa9a4e.jpg
